<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" dir="ltr">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Anime Game</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-ggOyR0iXCbMQv3Xipma34MD+dH/1fQ784/j6cY/iJTQUOhcWr7x9JvoRxT2MZw1T" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles-index.css">
  </head>
  <body>
  <h1>How well do you know your anime?</h1>
  <div class="center">
    <p>Hello fellow anime enthusiasts! I created this game as a fun way to test the breadth of your knowledge! <br></p>
    <p>First, pick a few genres that you want to test your expertise in!</p>
    <form action="/" method="post">
      <div class= "genresTable">
        <div class = "row no-gutters">
          <div class = "col-12 col-md-3"><button class = "genres btn btn-success shadow-none"type="button" value = "action" name="button">action</button></div>
          <div class = "col-12 col-md-3"><button class = "genres btn btn-success shadow-none"type="button" value = "comedy" name="button">comedy</button></div>
          <div class = "col-12 col-md-3"><button class = "genres btn btn-success shadow-none"type="button" value = "adventure"name="button">adventure</button></div>
          <div class = "col-12 col-md-3"><button class = "genres btn btn-success shadow-none"type="button" value = "drama" name="button">drama</button></div>
        </div>
        <div class = "row no-gutters">
          <div class = "col-12 col-md-3"><button class = "genres btn btn-success shadow-none"type="button" value = "slice of life" name="button">slice of life</button></div>
          <div class = "col-12 col-md-3"><button class = "genres btn btn-success shadow-none"type="button" value = "erotica" name="button">erotica</button></div>
          <div class = "col-12 col-md-3"><button class = "genres btn btn-success shadow-none"type="button" value = "fantasy" name="button">fantasy</button></div>
          <div class = "col-12 col-md-3"><button class = "genres btn btn-success shadow-none"type="button" value = "magic" name="button">magic</button></div>
        </div>
        <div class = "row no-gutters">
          <div class = "col-12 col-md-3"><button class = "genres btn btn-success shadow-none"type="button" value = "supernatural" name="button">supernatural</button></div>
          <div class = "col-12 col-md-3"><button class = "genres btn btn-success shadow-none"type="button" value = "horror" name="button">horror</button></div>
          <div class = "col-12 col-md-3"><button class = "genres btn btn-success shadow-none"type="button" value = "mystery" name="button">mystery</button></div>
          <div class = "col-12 col-md-3"><button class = "genres btn btn-success shadow-none"type="button" value = "psychological"name="button">psychological</button></div>
        </div>
        <div class="row no-gutters">
          <div class = "col-12 col-md-3"><button class = "genres btn btn-success shadow-none"type="button" value = "romance" name="button">romance</button></div>
          <div class = "col-12 col-md-3"><button class = "genres btn btn-success shadow-none"type="button" value = "science fiction" name="button">science fiction</button></div>
          <div class = "col-12 col-md-3"><button class = "genres btn btn-success shadow-none"type="button" value = "thriller" name="button">thriller</button></div>
          <div class = "col-12 col-md-3"><button class = "genres btn btn-success shadow-none"type="button" value = "tournament" name="button">tournament</button></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p>Next, which do you know better?</p>
      <div class="mOrA">
        <div class="row no-gutters">
          <div class = "col-12 col-md-6"><button class = "genres btn btn-success shadow-none"type="button" value = "anime" name="button">Anime</button></div>
          <div class = "col-12 col-md-6"><button class = "genres btn btn-success shadow-none"type="button" value = "manga" name="button">Manga</button></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p>Next, what level are you at?</p>
      <div class="mOrA">
        <div class="row no-gutters">
          <div class = "col-12 col-md-4"><button class = "difficulty btn btn-success shadow-none"type="button" value = "difficulty" name="button">Normal</button></div>
          <div class = "col-12 col-md-4"><button class = "difficulty btn btn-success shadow-none"type="button" value = "difficulty" name="button">Expert</button></div>
          <div class = "col-12 col-md-4"><button class = "difficulty btn btn-success shadow-none"type="button" value = "difficulty" name="button">Master</button></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p>Finally, put in your username so you can showoff your score!</p>
      <div class="inputField">
        <input type="text" name="username" placeholder="Player Name" autocomplete = "off">
        <button class = "btn btn-success btn-sm" type="button" name="button" value = "username">Submit</button>
      </div>
      <div class="play">
        <h6>Whenever you're ready, click play below!</h6>
        <button class = "btn btn-success btn-lg" type="button" name="button" value = "play">Play!</button>
      </div>
    </form>
  </div>
<script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.5.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="extra-index.js" charset="utf-8"></script>
  </body>
</html>
